Posted PR https://github.com/apache/hudi/pull/4447 based on the comments and discussion we had here. Please take a look. This is a generic version and the Log/Base file readers/writers pass in the needed key field for de-duplication and materialization.

And here is the much simplified version of the PR https://github.com/apache/hudi/pull/4449, where the HFile readers and writers do the key deduplication and materialization based on the hardcoded metadata payload key field 'key'.

> Facing the same issue. When will this be fixed? Is it part of the next minor release of 0.10.1 ?

@maddy2u Pls let me clarify: spark 3.2 support is a feature to be added, not an issue. 
And no, 0.10.1 will be a bug fix release, no new feature should be added there. This is expected in 0.11.0 major release.
